                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">REDMAN</hi>—
<rs id="t18550409-448-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18550409-448-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18550409-448-verdict-3" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>. Aged 21.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.</hi>
                  </rs>—
